B.YT=new A.W(B.Bg,["Eng. Yahya Al-Washali","Yahya Al-Washali \xb7 Engineer & Analyst","Work","Method","Stack","Contact","\u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0629","Software Engineer & System Analyst","Systems engineered for clarity, scale, and years of service.","Structure you can trust, interfaces you can read \u2014 from Flutter craft to SQL-backed platforms.","Discuss your roadmap","View selected work","The System Analyst lens","Quality and durability are not \u201cnice-to-haves.\u201d They are how you de-risk delivery, protect revenue, and keep teams fast.","Discover truth","Stakeholders, constraints, and data flows \u2014 documented before pixels or schemas.","Design for change","Modular boundaries and measurable requirements so the system can evolve safely.","Prove with evidence","Traceability from requirement \u2192 implementation \u2192 verification \u2014 especially under audit pressure.","Technology footprint","Tap a tile \u2014 this is the stack I use to ship serious products, not demos.","Selected engagements","Where analysis, integrity, and product craft had to agree \u2014 without noise.","Ready when you are","If you are planning a platform migration, a high-stakes product build, or a system that must not fail quietly \u2014 let\u2019s talk.","github.com/yhya123","\xa9 2026 Yahya Al-Washali","Back to portfolio"],t.w)
